            <footer class="post-footer">
            <div class="clearfix post-meta post-meta-bottom"> <span class="rtp-meta-cat">Categories: </span> <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/category/news-items/" title="View all posts in News Items" rel="tag">News Items</a>        <span class="rtp-post-comment-count"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2012/12/10/next-generation-drones-to-be-equipped-with-lasers/#comments" class="rtp-post-comment rtp-common-link"  title="Comment on Next Generation Drones to be Equipped with Lasers"><span>1</span> Comment</a></span><span class="post-tags"> Tags:  <span><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/darpa/" rel="tag">DARPA</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/general-atomics/" rel="tag">General Atomics</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/hellads-the-high-energy-liquid-laser-defense-system/" rel="tag">HELLADS — the High Energy Liquid Laser Defense System</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/mq-1-predators/" rel="tag">MQ-1 Predators</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/the-nation/" rel="tag">The Nation</a>, <a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/tag/time-magazine/" rel="tag">Time Magazine</a></span></span>                <span class="post-tags">Comments: </span><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2012/12/10/next-generation-drones-to-be-equipped-with-lasers/#comments">3</a> 
